  • Classes in statdoc.items used by statdoc.items 
    Class and Description
    CmdItem
    An Item representing a line in a script file.
    FileItem
    An Item to hold a link to a file.
    Item
    Item is the key class for all elements of analysis and provides a flexible container for information about an item and its children/relatives.
    MatchItem
    A special Item to match up parts that might not have been resolved, such as variables in script files where it is not yet known whether they reside in a specific data file.
    TokenItem
    Holds token information Main functionality is to provide a group (currently first letter) level identifier.
    VariableItem
    Variable information.
